        "description": "<p><a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/foodselfie/\">FoodSelfie</a> 是一款给美食添加各种人性化卡通贴纸的应用，比如胡子、眼睛、嘴巴等等。@Appinn</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/foodselfie/\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com//images/201605/first.jpg!o\" width=\"416\" height=\"739\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>还在正经的晒美食嘛？稍稍有点 out 了&#8230;</p>\n<p>用 <strong>FoodSelfie</strong> 可以给食物照添加各种拟人贴纸，比如眼睛、嘴巴、鼻子、放个屁什么的&#8230;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com//images/201605/screen322x572.jpeg!o\" width=\"322\" height=\"572\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>而添加贴纸后的食物立即显得与众不同：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com//images/201605/screen322x572-1.jpeg!o\" width=\"322\" height=\"572\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>嗯，其实呢，是挺有趣的，不过想要无限制使用贴纸需要内购解锁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://geo.itunes.apple.com/cn/app/foodselfie/id1082589391?mt=8&#038;at=1000l7mq&#038;ct=appinnpost\" style=\"display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(http://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/images/badges/en-us/badge_appstore-lrg.svg) no-repeat;width:165px;height:40px;\"></a></p>\n<hr />\n<a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/copyright/?utm_source=feeds&utm_medium=copyright&utm_campaign=feeds\" title=\"版权声明\">&#169;</a>2015 青小蛙 for <a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/?utm_source=feeds&utm_medium=appinn&utm_campaign=feeds\" title=\"本文来自小众软件\" >小众软件</a> | <a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/join-us/?utm_source=feeds&utm_medium=joinus&utm_campaign=feeds\" title=\"加入小众软件\">加入我们</a> | <a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/contribute/?utm_source=feeds&utm_medium=contribute&utm_campaign=feeds\" title=\"给小众软件投稿\" target=\"_blank\">投稿</a> | <a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/feeds-subscribe/?utm_source=feeds&utm_medium=feedsubscribe&utm_campaign=feeds\" title=\"可以分类订阅小众，Windows/MAC/游戏\" target=\"_blank\"><font color=\"red\">订阅指南</font></a> | <a href=\"http://appinn.wufoo.com/forms/eccae-aeeae/\">反馈</a> | <a href=\"http://hellohostnet.com/proxy.html\">代理</a>(优惠码 Appinn)<br />