        "title": "6 款在 iPhone 通知中心就能玩的游戏",
        "description": "<p>前几天青小蛙推荐了能在 <a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/tag/iphone/\">iPhone</a> 通知中心玩耍的游戏 <a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/steve-for-ios/\">跳跳龙</a>，觉得不过瘾，又发现 <a href=\"http://www.redmondpie.com/6-games-you-can-play-from-iphone-lock-screen-no-jailbreak-required/\">RedmondPie</a> 一下子推荐了 6 款在 iPhone 通知中心就能玩的小游戏。@Appinn</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/6-games-from-iphone-lock-screen/\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com/images/201604/screen322x572.jpg!o\" width=\"252\" height=\"298\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>在通知中心玩游戏一定是开发者无聊的时候想出来的，不够这个地方的确适合玩一些轻松的小游戏，用来打发看表的时间&#8230;</p>\n<h3><a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/steve-for-ios/\">Steve</a> – 在「通知中心」愉快的玩跳跳龙[iPhone]</h3>\n<p>这款青小蛙已经介绍过了，游戏是 Chrome 浏览器出错后的那只恐龙，不过 Steve 又增加了不少场景与角色，唯一的免费游戏，不玩都不行。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://geo.itunes.apple.com/cn/app/steve-jumping-dinosaur-widget/id1090617661?mt=8&amp;at=1000l7mq&amp;ct=appinnpost\" style=\"display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(http://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/images/badges/en-us/badge_appstore-lrg.svg) no-repeat;width:165px;height:40px;\"></a></p>\n<h3>Quickgets Snake 贪食蛇游戏</h3>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com/images/201604/screen322x572-1_5.jpeg!o\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>贪食蛇在通知中心太合适不过了，还能设置大小、颜色。唯一的问题可能有点费眼睛&#8230;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://geo.itunes.apple.com/cn/app/quickgets-snake-widget-app/id921404065?mt=8&#038;at=1000l7mq&#038;ct=appinnpost\" style=\"display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(http://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/images/badges/en-us/badge_appstore-lrg.svg) no-repeat;width:165px;height:40px;\"></a></p>\n<h3>Helicopter Widget &#8211; 直升机游戏</h3>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com/images/201604/screen322x572-2_3.jpeg!o\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>经典的直升机游戏，青小蛙已经记不清玩过没有了&#8230;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://geo.itunes.apple.com/us/app/helicopter-widget/id1003071363?mt=8&#038;at=1000l7mq&#038;ct=appinnpost\" style=\"display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(http://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/images/badges/en-us/badge_appstore-lrg.svg) no-repeat;width:165px;height:40px;\"></a></p>\n<h3>TicTacToe &#8211; OOXX 游戏</h3>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com/images/201604/screen322x572-3_1.jpeg!o\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>把 OOXX 连成一条线就好了，哈哈哈</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://geo.itunes.apple.com/us/app/tictactoe-widget-edition/id966408407?mt=8&#038;at=1000l7mq&#038;ct=appinnpost\" style=\"display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(http://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/images/badges/en-us/badge_appstore-lrg.svg) no-repeat;width:165px;height:40px;\"></a></p>\n<h3>Overglide &#8211; 纸飞机</h3>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com/images/201604/screen322x572-4.jpeg!o\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://geo.itunes.apple.com/us/app/overglide-widget-game/id930663613?mt=8&#038;at=1000l7mq&#038;ct=appinnpost\" style=\"display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(http://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/images/badges/en-us/badge_appstore-lrg.svg) no-repeat;width:165px;height:40px;\"></a></p>\n<h3>Minesweeper &#8211; 挖地雷有木有</h3>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://img3.appinn.com/images/201604/screen322x572-5.jpeg!o\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>最值得玩的就是这货了，挖地雷是多少人 Windows 的启蒙啊</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://geo.itunes.apple.com/us/app/minesweeper-widget-edition/id954323480?mt=8&#038;at=1000l7mq&#038;ct=appinnpost\" style=\"display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;background:url(http://linkmaker.itunes.apple.com/images/badges/en-us/badge_appstore-lrg.svg) no-repeat;width:165px;height:40px;\"></a></p>\n<p>这几款游戏，只有 Steve 是免费的，其他几款均售价 6 元，买个开心不贵啦。</p>\n<hr /><h2>相关阅读</h2><ul><li><a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/lock-screen-appinn-1/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Lock Screen Appinn &#8211; 屏幕密码锁[AHK]\">Lock Screen Appinn &#8211; 屏幕密码锁[AHK]</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.appinn.com/lock-screen-appinn-1-2/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Lock Screen Appinn – 屏幕密码锁[AHK] 更